* Wed May 03 2017 10:52:51 +0530 mbhangui@gmail.com 2.1-1.1.fc25
Release 2.1 Start 16/03/2017
1.  quoted svctool arguments and save install time arguments in variables/.options file
2.  update_tmprsadh, svctool, spec files, debian postinst, postrm - updated certificate
    location to sysconfdir/certs
3.  qmail-smtpd, qmail-remote - Env variable CERTDIR to override
    /etc/indimail/control for certificate location
4.  Permissions of supervise directory changed to onwer root:indimail 750
    for services using MAXDAEMONS
5.  renamed qmail-spamfifo service to qmail-logfifo
6.  added upgrade script upgrade.sh, local_upgrade.sh
7.  update_tmprsadh - added rsa2048.pem, dh2048.pem
8.  ucspi-tcp - control_readline() did not use CONTROLDIR. Caused problem with
    qmail_smtpd.so plugin which used the same symbol and was unable to load
    control files.
9.  fixed conf_dir variable getting clobbered by qmail-logfifo service creation.
10. create tlsservermethod control file in svctool --config=qmail
11. renamed functions in ucspi-tcp (rblsmtpd.so) to avoid duplicate symbols with
    qmail_smtpd.so
12. use RTLD_DEEPBIND (if present) in load_shared.c to avoid duplicate symbols
    when loading multiple shared libs
13. set DEFAULT_DOMAIN in qmail-send.25/variables as the hostname to handle
    double bounces better
14  qmail-todo, qmail-send - display null email address as <> in log_stat()
15. svctool --config=qmail - set envnoathost, defaulthost = hostname 
16. local_upgrade.sh - fix DEFAULT_HOST, QMAILDEFAULTHOST, envnoathost,
    defaulthost settings
17. svctool - MRTG graphs, added --mrtg option
18. local_upgrade.sh added FIFODIR env variable
19. replace dlopen() with dlmopen to keep tcpserver namespace private
20. added dlnamespace for using dlmopen()
21. tcpserver.c, prot.c - Changed data types for uid, gid to uid_t, gid_t
22. Bug with dlmopen(), glibc wrappers for setgroups, setgid, setuid - use syscall for setgroups, setgid, setuid
23. tcpserver - execute tcpserver_plugin after shedding root privileges
24. indimail-mta.postinst.in, indimail-mta.spec - upgraded softmem to 536870912
25. svctool - Fixed couriersslcache path
26. dlnamespace.c - added comments, replace back ':' character removed before
    string comparision
27. qmail-remote.c - fixed tls_quit() function. Avoid mixed usage of
    tls_quit() and quit() functions
28. qmail-remote.c, rrt.c - renamed ONTRANSIENT_REMOTE to ONTEMPORARY_REMOTE
29. qmail-rspawn.c Unset QMAILLOCAL in parent & not in child after vfork
30. perms of /etc/indimail and subdirectory changed to 2775
31. qmail-remote.c - use SMTPS if env variable SMTPS is set
32. qmail-queue.c - fixed envheader. variable x renamed to field_len and
    initialized to prevent skipping.
33. fixed sysconfdir and sysconfdir subdir permissions
34. use #ifdef HASDLMOPEN to use dlmopen() if present
35. tcpserver_plugin.c - use PLUGINn_DIR variable to change directory independent of PLUGINn_init
    env variable
36. create queue base directory in setup
37. report programs moved to libexecdir
38. surblqueue - fixed qmail-multi path
39. fixed search using hsearch in qmail-greyd.c
40. tcpserver - load_shared.c - print lmid only during reload
41. moved qmail-greyd, greydaemon, surblfilter, surbqueue to /usr/sbin
42. use lockfile .svlock in service directory to prevent multiple svscan
    to run on a service directory
43. dlnamespace.c, tcpserver_plugin.c, load_shared.c, pathexec_env.c added code
    to get namespace of shared libraries using env variables / envp variable
44. qmailctl.sh - added multilog rotate command
45. indimail-mta - install crontab entries for indimail-mta
46. qmail-smtpd - Updated documentation on LOGFILTER
47. qmail-smtpd - renamed LOGFILTER_FD to LOGFD
48. shutdown indimail service in preun
49. (rpm, debian) - use svok to figure out if service is up
50. svctool - fixed inverted cname-lookup
51. (rpm, debian) - removed duplicate calls to shutdown indimail service
52. (rpm, debian) - use sed to edit inittab
53. added svctool man page
54. fixed sysconfdir variable in debian scripts
55. OSX indimail.plist - fixed svscanboot path
56. fixed DESTDIR in qmail-1.03, ucspi-tcp-1.03 Makefile, setup.c
57. fixed tlsclientmethod path in qmail-remote
58. cleanq.c - refactored code. added checks for safety
59. setup.c, instcheck.c - added logdir
